## Owl (Liang)

* Optimsations of modules:
- sparse complex matrix module
- Fast Fourier Transforms
- Potential for a topic module - working together with Ben Caterall who is working on it for his Part II project.

* First version of Owl released via OPAM and included in MirageOS documentation.
* Implemented a simple LDA model for Owl

Meetings with Owl users and identified potential directions to focus on before the end of the year:
- advanced support for multi-dimensional array
- auto gradient derivation functions

[Blog post](https://github.com/ryanrhymes/owl/wiki/Manipulate-Matrices-in-Owl) on how to use Owl to manipulate matrices.

